      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly way to get behind the wheel? This car is a diamond in the rough, ready for someone with a vision to bring it back to its former glory! While it currently shows significant wear and will require some mechanical and cosmetic attention, it remains a fantastic opportunity for a DIY enthusiast. Grab this chance to own a vehicle with great potential at a price that leaves plenty of room for your personal touch!",
