    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in 'as-is' condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows heavy wear, including noticeable paint oxidation, several deep scratches, and a few dents on the body panels. Inside, the upholstery is worn with some tears, and the electronics are inconsistent. Mechanically, the car runs but needs immediate repairs to the suspension and cooling system to be reliable for daily use. It\u2019s a candidate for a full restoration or for someone looking for a project vehicle.",
