    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolutely mint, showroom condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it was first delivered. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine condition, still smelling new with no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with an open checkbook. For a collector or a buyer seeking a 'like-new' experience, this car offers unparalleled quality and reliability.",
