    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's looking for a great new home. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs beautifully\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it. I've taken great care of it, so you can just hop in and go! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin or have any questions at all!",
      "price": 32000.0,
