    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. Power is delivered via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS service. The suspension retains its factory-spec handling characteristics with updated bushings, and the braking system features ventilated rotors with firm pedal feedback. While the chassis shows minor signs of road use consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and atmospheric induction remain sharp. This is a driver-focused machine with a linear power band that pulls strongly to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Maintenance records available. Reliable performance. No mechanical issues.",
